          "src": "data:image/svg+xml;base64,",
          "alt": "Streaming token flow: client sends POST /chat with stream=true; LLM engine produces tokens one at a time; API server forwards each token as a Server-Sent Event (SSE); client renders text progressively. TTFB (time-to-first-byte) measures latency to the first SSE chunk."
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
